data.description: Welcome to one of the most serene neighborhoods in Chelsea! This home sits on almost half an acre with no HOA! The privacy of the trees in the backyard provides a peaceful tranquility. The large screened-in back porch has a vaulted ceiling and is the perfect spot for drinking your morning coffee or winding down at night. There's a custom covered grilling station and a flagstone patio area with a built-in fire pit! The main level includes a living room w/ a gas fireplace, a light-filled dining room, an updated eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops, tile backsplash, a gas stove, & breakfast bar. 3 Bedrooms are also on the main level. The Primary Suite is on the right side of the home and has a door to walk out onto the deck! The other 2 bedrooms are on the opposite side of the house and share a full bath. Downstairs is ideal for those Game Days or a great spot for teen hangs, complete with a rec room, a wet bar, a full bath & the 4th bedroom. Forest Oaks Elementary + Chelsea High
